###############################################################################
# OBJECTIVE
###############################################################################
Measure every interactive element in the app; document which are below the
44px Apple HIG minimum; categorize by severity; provide fix plan.

###############################################################################
# SCOPE
###############################################################################
Audit scope (all files in navitrack-apps/react-app/src/):

1. UI Components:
   - button.tsx (all size variants: default h-10, sm h-9, lg h-11, icon h-10)
   - input.tsx (current height)
   - switch.tsx (Radix Switch dimensions)
   - select.tsx (trigger height)
   - glass-button.tsx, glass-card.tsx, glass-input-wrapper.tsx

2. App Components:
   - mobile-shell.tsx (bottom nav tabs — py-2, icon h-5)
   - mobile-header.tsx (header h-12, back button, right action)
   - theme-toggle.tsx (h-8 w-8 = 32px ← PROBLEM)
   - bottom-select-modal.tsx (list items, cancel button)
   - date-range-picker.tsx (calendar cells, time slider, done/cancel)
   - logo.tsx (if tappable)

3. All 9 Screens:
   - login-screen.tsx (inputs h-12, button h-14 — OK)
   - objects-screen.tsx (search h-10, vehicle rows py-3, settings icon)
   - settings-screen.tsx (buttons h-11, h-12, h-14, toggles)
   - tracking-screen.tsx (event toggles h-11 w-11, vehicle select h-11, sliders h-2)
   - reports-screen.tsx (dropdown buttons h-11, build button h-14)
   - map-screen.tsx (settings button)
   - object-details-screen.tsx (tabs, apply button, event toggles)
   - select-objects-screen.tsx (search h-10, checkboxes h-7 w-7 ← PROBLEM, apply h-14)
   - account-security-screen.tsx (form elements)

###############################################################################
# MEASUREMENT METHOD
###############################################################################
For each interactive element:
1. Record: component, file, line, current size (px), touch-friendly (Y/N)
2. Classify severity:
   - 🔴 CRITICAL: < 32px (unusable on mobile)
   - 🟡 WARNING: 32-43px (below minimum)
   - 🟢 OK: ≥ 44px (meets Apple HIG)
3. Note if spacing between adjacent targets < 8px

###############################################################################
# KNOWN PROBLEMS (from code scan)
###############################################################################
problems:
  critical:
    - ThemeToggle: h-8 w-8 = 32px (need 44px)
    - SelectObjects checkboxes: h-7 w-7 = 28px (need 44px)
    - Range slider tracks: h-2 = 8px (need touch padding)
  warning:
    - Bottom nav tabs: ~40px (py-2) needs min-h-[44px]
    - Search inputs: h-10 = 40px (need h-12 = 48px)
    - Button size "sm": h-9 = 36px (need h-11 = 44px)
    - Button size "default": h-10 = 40px (need h-12 = 48px)
    - Button size "icon": h-10 w-10 = 40px (need h-11 w-11 = 44px)
    - BottomSelectModal list items: no explicit min-height

###############################################################################
# DELIVERABLES
###############################################################################
output:
  - S45-TOUCH-AUDIT.md with:
    - Complete table of all interactive elements with sizes
    - Severity classification (red/yellow/green)
    - Spacing issues between adjacent targets
    - Recommended fix for each problem
    - Priority order for fixes

###############################################################################
# ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA
###############################################################################
verify:
  - [ ] Every interactive element in the app is documented
  - [ ] Each element has measured height/width in px
  - [ ] Severity classification applied
  - [ ] Fix recommendations provided
  - [ ] No interactive element missed
